<br>
My issue with sword in general and  skalds in particular is that due to our swing speed and lack of reliable defence, there is no obvious advantage to using any other styles.  And unlike the famous dragonfang, annhialation, and leviathon there is no clearly superior positional or reactionary that we can use depending on different situations.<br>
